Title: Adaptive Esports Tournament: Richard Jacob’s
Description:
Welcome to Brooklyn, NY, home of Richard Jacobs (@breadwinner1007).

Richard is a member of the fearless esports team, @the_quadgods. Hungry for competition, Richard’s tenacious spirit drives him to keep pushing further and further in the esports space.

@the_quadgods organization is was founded by a group of 8 quadriplegic gamers with the goal to integrate and highlight all gamers with disabilities as serious esports competitors. Richard represented the Quad Gods in last fall’s tournament, bringing his passion to the Rocket League arena. 

Sign up for the next Adaptive Esports Tournament in our link in bio!

Description:
In celebration of World Oceans Day, we’re excited to announce our partnership with sustainability startup @clearbothk, to redefine the way we clean our oceans.

Together with Clearbot’s prototype and our inhouse design and engineering expertise, we developed a newly designed and fully automated ocean cleaning robot. Built with cutting edge AI and machine learning capabilities, it detects and collects marine plastic within two meters in rough waters. Learn more about the Clearbot robot at the link in our bio.

Title: Apex 15X Product Overview
Description:
Our flagship 15-inch laptop, the APEX 15X is designed to bring to you premium features in a ultraportable form factor. Featuring NVIDIA's latest Ampere-based RTX 3070 graphics card along with an 8 core processor, the APEX 15X delivers gaming performance at a sweet spot price point.
In this product overview we go over some of the key highlights that make the APEX 15X an award-winning laptop - rated 9/10 and awarded the Editor’s Choice by Geek Culture! The APEX 15X is packed with features such as a ultra-sharp QHD 165hz display and mechanical keyboard. Find out why the APEX 15X is the ultimate 15-inch gaming laptop.

Key Features Includes:
- Aluminum Alloy Chassis 
- Intel®? Core™? i7-10870H Processor (8 Core 10th Generation Processor)
- NVIDIA GEFORCE RTX 3070 8GB GDDR6 (80-105W Boost)
- 15.6 Inch 165HZ QHD Premium IPS Display (2560 x 1440)
- Up to 32GB DDR4 3200MHZ (Operates at 2933mhz with Intel Notebooks)
- Premium Enthusiast Grade Thermal Compound
- Per Key RGB Mechanical Keyboard
- Up to 4TB SSD Storage
- INTEL AX201 (Wi-Fi 6) + Bluetooth
- Up to 3 Years Parts Warranty
- 2.1kg

For those of you looking for a brand new Intel powered rig, we've got exciting news! 

We're committed to always staying ahead of the game, adopting next generation technology and ensuring our users always have the edge. With the arrival of 11th gen Intel processors and new 500 series motherboards, we're effectively phasing out the old Intel 10th generation processors to move forward as quickly as possible with their newest lineup!

Our Intel based ready to ship (RTS) packages are now configured with brand new INTEL 11th gen processors and B560/Z590 motherboards! With improved single core and gaming performance, combined with high speed ram support on the new B560M motherboards that previous generation b460 and h410 Intel boards did not allow for, these builds are looking better than ever! (Not to mention most of them are priced similar to previous 10th gen packages that are now being phased out. ??)

So if you're looking to get an Intel based build, do check out our 11th generation and 500 series motherboard RTS packages. We've worked hard to equip them with best in the most elite components at each price point!

Exciting news!! ?? The brand new B560 motherboards for Intel builds have arrived, and having tested them hands on at our labs, these boards are an absolute must have if you're considering an i5 based custom PC (or i7 10700F for that matter!).

With support for high speed memory, such as 3200mhz or 3600mhz modules, the B560 boards will allow you to pair an i5 10400F, 10600KF or i7 10700F with fast memory, resulting in better gaming performance (up to 5% in some of our tests!). Last generation B460 and H410 boards are LOCKED at 2666mhz when paired with an i5 chip, or 2933mhz with higher end chips, even when if you are using a high speed RAM modules. 

So if you're considering an i5 10400F or 10600KF for your next PC build, do keep the B560 board in mind!

The B560 and Z590 board options are now available for customisation with any AFTERSHOCK PC, and we've also upgraded our INTEL based ready to ship builds with B560 boards, making them fair superior to the other Intel based, H410 and B460 builds - with superior RAM speeds and gaming performance!
